{
  "stem": "11964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I was there at the bin, I heard shouting in German, [GERMAN], somebody escaped, and people were running.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The SS was running up and down the stairs, and I heard the dogs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said to myself, I'm not going to scheme anymore because I knew that wherever I was going I would not return from.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was just sitting there in that coal bin, squatting, and almost fearful to breathe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember that I was listening to the noises, and, and I was-- I, I-- really, I was numb.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't scheme any longer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when I realized that all the noises abated, and I sort of heard wagons going back and forth on the street, I realized that the streets were free and that people were moving about.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I just crawled out of the bin and shook all the coal off myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't recall what I was wearing at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was very numb.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was going down the stairs, and I said, I just won't look back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I will just go straight ahead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was just about two, two and a half blocks from where the Loszeks lived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I summoned all the energy and all the nerve, and I went upstairs to the Loszeks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Loszek opened the door, and she says-- I'll never forget it-- Jesus Christ, look at her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, is Tobcia here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she says, yes, she's sound and safe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she had her isolated in a room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She put a big chifferobe against a door because it seems that she had some neighbors coming in, and she was afraid that they would snoop her out.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
